verbose_text: Small interfering RNA knock-down of the multi-functional transcription factor (TF), nuclear factor kappa-light-chain-enhancer of activated B cells (NF-kappaB) 1, in human retinal endothelial cells significantly reduced a tumor necrosis factor (TNF)-alpha-induced increase in ICAM-1 expression, but did not alter constitutive ICAM-1 expression.
